OL,5,BCLIMATE ACTION NETWORK    C February 24
OL,7,GThe meeting will focus on the key      
OL,8,Goutcome of Kyoto with presentations by 
OL,9,Genvironmental groups who took part in  
OL,10,Gthe negotiations.                      
OL,12,GIt will cover what the protocol means  
OL,13,Gand the next steps for the UN climate  
OL,14,Gnegotiations. Keynote speaker: Rt Hon  
OL,15,GJohn Gummer.                           
OL,17,GContact: Chris Gore on 0171-836 1110   
