OL,5,CTHE TELETEXT CAMELL EXPEDITION         
OL,7, Intrepid explorer Alexandra Hughes     
OL,8, Bannister set off in December last year
OL,9, to go around Australia on camel-back.  
OL,11, Teletext is sponsoring the 31-year-old 
OL,12, from Lyminster, Hants, as she spends   
OL,13, two years covering the 17,000 km route.
OL,15, The CAMELL (Circumnavigating Australia 
OL,16, Motivating Environmentalists at Local  
OL,17, Levels) expedition aims to raise green 
OL,18, and other issues. Green Scene will     
OL,19, feature her progress, but for more...  
